resources.string: Ukuze uye ekhaya, swayiphela ngokushesha phezulu usuka phansi. Ukuze ufinyelele Ibha Yomsebenzi, swayiphela kancane phezulu kusukela phansi. Ukuze ushintshe ama-app, swayiphela phezulu kusukela ngaphansi, ubambe, bese uyakhulula. Ukuze ubuyele emuva, swayipha kusukela kunqenqema langakwesokunxele noma kwesokudla.
Sondeza le divayisi eduze kwe-Pixel Tablet yakho bese uphinde uyazama.
Vula ikhesi lama-earbuds bese ulisondeza ku-Pixel Tablet yakho, bese uyazama futhi.
